title: [1991] Stan Getz & Kenny Barron - People Time (320kbps)
description:
Fantastic live album from Kenny Barron and Stan Getz. Kenny Barron on piano and Stan Getz on saxophone. The last recording with Stan Getz, as he died just a few months later. Quality is 320kbps.
